SimpleAV aims on simplifing you job on decoding videos.
It is released under LGPL v3.

Current version is 0.1.0b, based on libav v0.7.

The next version may features:
 * precise seeking
 * correct down-mixing

Start with "saplayer-old.c" if you are interested. :-P
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMPILATION:

    1. make
    2. sudo make install

Then have fun!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USING SIMPLEAV:

To use SimpleAV in your own program, just add '-lSimpleAV' when calling gcc.
Like this:

    $ gcc saplayer-old.c -lSimpleAV -lSDL `pkg-config --libs libavcodec libavformat libavutil libswscale`